net.bytebuddy.dynamic.loading

Class MultipleParentClassLoader.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.bytebuddy.dynamic.loading.MultipleParentClassLoader.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    MultipleParentClassLoader

    public static class MultipleParentClassLoader.Builder
extends Object
    A builder to collect class loader and that creates a MultipleParentClassLoader only if multiple or no ClassLoaders are found in the process. If exactly a single class loader is found, this class loader is returned. All class loaders are applied in their collection order.
